        </sec>
      </sec>
      <sec id="Sec6">
        <title>Stability of the system</title>
        <p>From the description in Subsection&#xA0;<xref rid="Sec4" ref-type="sec">2.1.1</xref> (see also Fig.&#xA0;<xref rid="Fig1" ref-type="fig">1</xref>) it is clear that the number of semi-urgent slots waiting at the start of week <italic>n</italic>&#x2009;+&#x2009;1 equals the number of semi-urgent slots that arrived during week <italic>n</italic> plus the number of surplus semi-urgent slots of week <italic>n</italic>:
