      </sec>
      <sec id="Sec8">
        <title>Performance measures</title>
        <p>We are particularly interested in the expected number of canceled elective slots per work week (<inline-formula id="IEq9"><alternatives><tex-math id="M16">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
