      <sec id="Sec9">
        <title>Cost structure</title>
        <p>Let <italic>C</italic><sub><italic>e</italic></sub> and <italic>C</italic><sub><italic>c</italic></sub> be the costs of one empty semi-urgent slot and one canceled elective slot. The expected total costs then equal
