				\begin{document}$$ \begin{array}{rll} \mathbb{P}(w_n|w_{n-1},a) &amp;= &amp; \mathbb{P}(R1_{n-1}=w1_n-w2_{n-1}+a) \\ &amp;&amp; \times \,\mathbb{P}(R2_{n-1}\! =\! w2_n - (w1_{n-1}-s+a)^+), \\ &amp;&amp; w1_n&lt;m, w1_n+w2_n&lt;2m, \end{array} $$\end{document}</tex-math><graphic xlink:href="10729_2010_9127_Article_Equn.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula>and <inline-formula id="IEq13"><alternatives><tex-math id="M29">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
